iscount to its SMA200 and shows strong fundamental health with a 48.5% ROE and a compelling forward P/E of 19.22. Despite recent price depreciation, the high profit margins and revenue growth suggest a robust long-term outlook.\n\n    *   JSON only? Yes.\n    *   One action? Yes.\n    *   Reasoning 2-4 sentences? Yes.", "finish_reason": "stop"}',112411,NULL,'2026-07-16T00:49:54+00:00');
