ove both SMA50 and SMA200, supported by a compelling forward P/E of 15.01. While strategic expansion news is positive, the RSI of 63.85 and flat 3-month returns indicate a period of consolidation, making HOLD the most prudent action.\"}", "finish_reason": "stop"}',303015,NULL,'2026-07-17T21:54:21+00:00');
